refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public boolMongoCollection::setReadPreference intread_preference arraytags
See the read preferences section of this manual for further information.

  &reftitle.examples;

   MongoCollection::setReadPreference tag set array syntax example


<?php

$m = new Mongo();
$c = $m->test->users;

// Prefer the nearest server in the "east" data center also used for reporting,
// but fall back to a server in the "west" data center
$c->setReadPreference(Mongo::RP_NEAREST, array(
    array('dc' => 'east', 'use' => 'reporting'),
    array('dc' => 'west'),
));
